

Url : /api/login
Method : POST
POST Data : [username, password]
Description : Login action for system user
Response : JSON user information
Example :

{
    user : {
        firstname: "R-JAY",
        lastname: "CRUZ",
        bday: "1994-03-17",
    }
}

----------------------------------
Url : /api/tickets
Method : GET
Description : Display all assigned tickets if ITD, else display all created tickets
Response : JSON
Example :
{
    tickets : {
        *ticket_no: [
            category : "F2 System"
            level: "HIGH",
            severity : "CRITICAL"
        ] ,
        *ticket_no: [
            category : "F2 System"
            level: "HIGH",
            severity : "CRITICAL"
        ]
    }
}


Url : /api/